"De deugd is een houding die ons in staat stelt ons handelingen voor te nemen, en die het midden houdt in relatie tot ons, een midden zoals dat bepaald is door een overleg en wel zoals een verstandig mens het zou bepalen."
(https://nl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deugd)

a virtuous being defines the habit of a constant behaviour 
that always looks for benefit and avoids detriment of the self individual, 
this behaviour drives the cellular structure to the most appropiate action of its own scence. 
the virtue is born in the encounter of the mind and heart, 
like the racionalization of the our irrational souls

the virtue is the habit of a constant behaviour that searches benefit and avoids detriment of the individual, this behaviour drives cellular structures to the most appropiate action of its scence. the virtue are born in the encounter of the mind and heart, like the racionalization of the our irrational souls

la virtud es el habito de la accion constante que busca el beneficio y evita el detrimento del propio individuo, son acciones que llevan nuestra estructura celular a la accion mas apropiada para su propia esencia. nacen del encuentro de nuestra mente y corazon, como si fueran conclusiones formadas racionalizando el alma irracional

virtue is the habit of constant action that seeks benefit and avoids the detriment of the individual, they are actions that take our cellular structure to the most appropriate action for its own essence. they are born from the encounter of our mind and heart, as if they were conclusions formed by rationalizing the irrational soul

